ion-spare, sinuous, vigorous in its narration, and translucent in its poetry-makes a masterpiece accessible to everyone.    aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Apr 2021) 0aDragonsvPoetry. 0aEpic poetry, English (Old). 0aHeroesvPoetry. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aMitchell, Stephen.40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300231397423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300231397.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles